    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.PkYYoSwGjKt9BiTo]{Weapon Group: Melee Weapons}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">The buzz baton is a non-collapsible truncheon with a point capable of emanating a powerful electric shock. Basic damage is bludgeoning. As part of a hit, you can use a cell charge and either inflict +2 lightning damage, or replace the entire bludgeoning damage with lightning damage.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Buzz baton </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5,000 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 111px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1d6 bludgeoning / lightning </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 33px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 134px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Bonus (+1), finesse, light, pincher, reload (20-M),<br />TL3</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.qB35DS5654aWtgir]{Finesse}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.bY9owuVfWrNWp8NV]{Light}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.nEUBgd3Yxs3OUtvD]{Pincher}&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.QjoW3JNAsq3eJt4s]{Reload 20-M} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-equipment.lmAMoPPYbIwgHfGl]{Battry Cell, Medium}</p>",
